name: GLBanners
tag_list: facebook-banners, facebook, banners, profile, page, design, custom
overview:
http://GLBanners.com provides cool Facebook banners for your Facebook profile page, for free.

With Facebook’s new profile page design and the addition of the tagged images header on the profile page, you can now add cool banner designs there from GLBanners.com First, you find a Facebook Banner that you like. After find a banner, you can automatically install it by click the “Upload banner to Facebook” button; when clicked, the banner will automatically upload simple and easily. You can also manually install Facebook banners by saving and upload the 5 pre-cut images of the banner. GLBanners.com also provides help and support for anything regarding banners, you can also request custom Facebook banners.
